==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Subduple
<hw>Sub"du*ple</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Math.)</fld>
<def>Indicating one part of two; in the ratio of one to two.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><cs><col><b>Subduple ratio</b></col>, <cd>the ratio of 1 to 2: thus,
3:6 is a <xex>subduple ratio</xex>, as 6:3 is a <xex>duple
ratio</xex>.</cd></cs>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Subduplicate</ent>⟦br⟧
